	<DIR>Technical Director:			4508<BR>
	Executive Assistant:		4516<BR>
	Special Program Assistant:	4921<BR>
	Fax:					4924</DIR>

For initial discussions with a Science Officer, forward your request by e-mail or call or fax the Executive Assistant or the Special Program Assistant for referral to the appropriate individual.<P><HR><P><A HREF="http://www.ehis.navy.mil:80/onreur.htm">Return to previous page</A>


