 <B>Appendix B: Meeting Itinerary</B><P>

<B>Monday, 7 October:  Farnborough</B><BR>
Escort and Coordinator: David Pask, DERA Customer Manager, TQ2 Programmes<BR>
Familiarization Tour<BR>
