<I><A NAME="34">(34)</A></I>  We were told that the term "Efficiency scrutiny" derives from a technique successfully employed by Derek Rayner, Chairman and CEO of Marks and Spencer.  The basic idea is to identify an area of work where savings appear possible, and bring in a young turk from another area or sector to perform a focused efficiency review.<BR>
