John D. Lewis<BR>
   at<BR> 
 TEL: +44-171-514-4369<BR>  
FAX: +44-171-514-4924<BR> 
E-mail address: jlewis@onreur.navy.mil<P>
 International mail address:<BR>  
John D. Lewis<BR>  
