<H3>1995 European Conference Update</H3>  The following is a list of
upcoming European Conferences & Meetings in the area of biochemistry,
biophysics, neural networks, neuroscience, artificial intelligence,
medicine, toxicology, immunology, environmental sciences and psychology.
 NATO conferences are not included.  If you would like to advertise a
European meeting not on this list, please send me the information and I
will append it.<P>
<B>7th European Congress on Biotechnology</B><BR>
