of Reinforcement Theory of Polymer Composites. <BR> - 93 - 01 - 00168 -
Novikov Sergei Petrovich - Methods of integrating systems of
hydrodynamic type and constructing of Hamiltonian formalism. <BR> - 93
- 01 - 00171 - Evtushik Leonid Evgenievich - The global modification and
the description of Cartan - Laptev method as a universal algebraic -
differential apparatus in geometry and its application to the modern
investigation of actual structures in geometry and mathematical physics.
<BR> - 93 - 01 - 00179 - Toponogov Victor Andreevich - Problems of
stability of geometric and differential topological properties of
