Evseevich - Study of brain mechanisms of coordination rearrangement
during motor learning and their neuronal network modelling. <BR> - 93 -
04 - 06281 - Ginter Evgeney Konstantinovich - The effects of genetic
drift and selection on distribution of autosomal recessive disorders in
the populations of Russia. <BR> - 93 - 04 - 06296 - Tsalolikhin Semyon
Iakovlevich - Freshwater invertebrates of Russia and adjacent lands (in
3 vol.). <BR> - 93 - 04 - 06297 - Andriashev Anatoly Petrovich - Fishes
of the Arctic. <BR> - 93 - 04 - 06329 - Golitchenkov Vladimir
Alexandrovich - Analysis of patomorphogeny in transgenic fish. <BR> -
93 - 04 - 06362 - Shestakov Sergey Vasilievich - Genetics and gene
engineering of nitrogen-fixing and phototropic bacteria. 
<P>EXAMPLES FROM INSTITUTE IDENTIFICATION</P>93-01-00007 - Institute of problems of transfer of the information of RAS- 101447, Moscow, street.
Ermolovoi, 19 <BR> 93-01-00008 - Institute of the system analysis of
