Abrosimov G., Buzhinskij 01., Pulinets T., Skvortsova Al. "Line Co. Ltd. " Diagnostic System Based on Copper Vapour Laser.<P>

Grezev C., Zelenov E., Morozenkov A. Unique Desigh of Sungle Mode C02 Laser and Laser Technolodical Processes Development by the "Lasernye Komplexy" .<P>

Surface Physics.<BR>
Lonkov Yu., Moskalev 1. Precision Grinding of the Solid
by Pitch Polisher with Surface-Charged Abrasive.<BR>
Trofimenko V. "Line Company Ltd" High Speed Photography<BR>
Buzhinskij Ol., Tugarinov S., Azizov En., Trofimenko
V.,Line Company Ltd" Ion implantation pyrolytic heron nitride.<BR>
