Company Ltd"  Modified Graphite and Carbonic Fibre
Materials.<P>

<B>5. Proceedings</B><BR>
Proceedings can be made available upon request. Papers
in the proceedings are published unedited from the
camera ready manuscripts.<P>

<B>6. Chapter formation</B><BR>
The participants of the workshop unanimously approved
of the idea of creating either an association or a fund
aimed at uniting the efforts of private companies in
the CIS to develop complex, multi-purpose technologies
and equipment.<BR>
Such an association will perform the following tasks:
representation, information, advertising and
publishing, project expertise, and establishment of
temporary teams from participating companies for
accomplishment of complex R&D.<P>

