   223 Old Marylebone Road<BR>
   London NW1 5TH<BR>
   Telephone: 44-171-514-4413 (Wilcox)<BR>
                    44-171-514-4260 (Mecholsky)<BR>
   Fax:          44-171-723-6359 (Wilcox and Mecholsky)<BR>
   E-mail:      bwilcox@onreur.navy.mil<BR>
                   jmecholsky@onreur.navy.mil<P>

   For additional information about the research program at the Institute for Advanced Materials-Joint Research Centre please contact:<P>

   Dr. G. Ceccone<BR>
   Institute for Advanced Materials<BR>
   P.O. Box 2<BR>
   1755 ZG Petten, Netherlands<BR>
   telephone:  +31 224 565171<BR>
   fax:            +31 224 562036<BR>
   e-mail: ceccone@fs-iam-1.jrc.nl<P>

   For additional information about the research program at the National Ceramic Centre, ECN please contact:<P>

   Dr. L.A. Correia<BR>
   Netherlands Energy Research Foundation, ECN<BR>
   Westerduinweg 3,<BR>
   P.O. Box 1,<BR>
   1755 ZG Petten, Netherlands<BR>
   telephone: +31 224 564535<BR>
   fax:           +31 224 563615<BR>
   E-mail:      correia@ecn.nl<P><HR><P>


The Office of Naval Research, Europe is dedicated to providing current information on science and technology development in European countries.  In order to better meet your needs, our staff are very much interested in knowing of your specific science and technology interests.  Please let us know what they are.  Furthermore, if there are others you are aware of, who may have interest in these newsletters, please pass their e-mail addresses to us and we will add them to the distribution list.  ONR Europe is on the World Wide Web.  Our home page contains information about European activities, conferences, and other newsletters.  Find us at http://www.ehis.navy.mil/<P><HR><P>

The opinions and assessments in this report are solely those of the author and do not necessarily reflect official US Government, US Navy or ONREUR positions.<P><HR><P><A HREF="http://www.ehis.navy.mil/onrnews.htm">Return to ONREUR Newsletters</A>

 
  
