	Telephone:	44 171 514-4964<BR>
	FAX:		44 171 723-6359<BR>
	E-Mail		aweinstein@onreur.navy.mil<P>

Address for a personal copy of the program/abstracts and information on future conferences, feel free to contact<BR>
	The Challenger Society for Marine Science<BR>
	Southampton Oceanography Centre<BR>
	Empress Dock<BR>
	Southampton S014 3ZH  Hampshire<BR>
	Telephone:	44 1703 595000<BR>
	FAX:		44 1703 596149<P>

<P><HR><P>
