<H3>Newsletter #32 <BR>
"Technologies of the 21th Century: R&D Strategy of the German Ministry of Research and Technology" (Part 2)<BR>
27-May-94</H3>
<B>Content:</B>

<OL>
<LI>1. Focus on SENSOR TECHNOLOGY
<DD>+ Biosensors in medicine
